- cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is the most likely category as the paper deals with artificial neural networks and their tuning.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper discusses a control algorithm for adjusting weights in a supervised learning context.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with a method for improving the performance of artificial neural networks.
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is a possible category as the paper frames the problem of tuning weights as a feedback control tracking problem.
- cs.SD (Software Engineering) is less likely but still possible as the paper may discuss implementation details of the proposed algorithm.
